results.deck: Saffire Corporation was a former video game developer that was based in American Fork, Utah. Their last title, Thunderbirds was released in 2004.
results.description:
Overview

Saffire Corporation started out as Cygnus Multimedia. Cygnus Multimedia was founded in the 1990's by Les Pardew. When the company was first founded it operated out of Les' basement and consisted of only six employees.

The name of Cygnus Multimedia would be changed to Saffire Corporation in 1994.
